title: Aruatu 6 Inch Pink Wood Letters for Wall Decor: Standing & Decorative Large Letters for Craft & Home Party Projects
features: [Wooden Alphabet Letters]: Aruatu each package includes a single wooden letter, perfect for personalizing your décor. Use them to create custom messages like "Happy Holidays" or display names.

【Smooth and Comfortable】: Crafted from wood, Aruatu Unfinished Wood Letters boast a smooth surface that's gentle on your hands. The pleasant texture enhances comfort and tactile experience. Additionally, there's no strong odor, making them perfect for DIY projects.

【Durability and Stability】: Aruatu Paintable Letters for crafts are constructed from high-quality density fiberboard, ensuring their sturdiness and dependability. They resist breaking or fading, allowing the letters to stand independently on your desk without requiring additional support.

【Unleash Your Creativity】: Aruatu Unfinished Wooden Letters maintain their natural wood color, making them ideal for painting, carving, adding lace decorations, or preserving their original appearance. Share the joy of DIY with family and friends, creating cherished memories together.
[Versatile Décor]: Aruatu wooden letter suitable for any occasion—holidays, birthdays, parties, or rustic-themed events. These letters add a charming touch to walls, doors, and more.
